prompt: Find me images of Aurelia aurita
result1:
SELECT TOP 10 i.url, i.id as image_id, b.concept, b.id
FROM images i
JOIN bounding_boxes b ON i.id = b.image_id
WHERE b.concept = 'Aurelia aurita'
FOR JSON PATH

prompt: Find me images of moon jellyfish in Monterey bay and depth less than 5k meters
result2:
SELECT TOP 10 i.url, i.id as image_id, b.concept, b.id, i.depth_meters
FROM images i
JOIN bounding_boxes b ON i.id = b.image_id
JOIN marine_regions mr ON i.latitude BETWEEN mr.min_latitude AND mr.max_latitude
    AND i.longitude BETWEEN mr.min_longitude AND mr.max_longitude
WHERE b.concept = 'Aurelia aurita'
    AND mr.name = 'Monterey bay'
    AND i.depth_meters < 5000
FOR JSON PATH

prompt: What is the total number of images of Aurelia aurita in Monterey bay in the database
result1:
SELECT COUNT(i.id) as TotalImages
FROM images i
JOIN marine_regions mr ON i.latitude BETWEEN mr.min_latitude AND mr.max_latitude
    AND i.longitude BETWEEN mr.min_longitude AND mr.max_longitude
WHERE i.media_type = 'image'
    AND i.valid = 1
    AND mr.name = 'Monterey bay'
    AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM bounding_boxes bb
        WHERE bb.image_id = i.id
            AND bb.concept = 'Aurelia aurita'
    );
